15:20.999 --> 15:22.442
Thank you, Missy.

15:22.567 --> 15:26.779
Moving on to lot 44,
an Australian surf vacation.

15:26.904 --> 15:29.345
We are very close to our goal,

15:29.511 --> 15:33.599
