- Idiots.

16:20.479 --> 16:22.481
8,500.
Put that down.

16:22.647 --> 16:24.462
- $10,000.
- 10,500--

16:24.587 --> 16:25.693
give me the paddles.

16:25.859 --> 16:26.819
